title: Old and New Challenges for Central Banking in West Africa
itunes:author: Piroska Nagy Mohacsi, Dr Angela Lusigi, Dr Ernest Addison
description: Contributor(s): Piroska Nagy Mohacsi, Dr Angela Lusigi, Dr Ernest Addison | This event explores the financial and economic prospects for the region’s emerging economies, the impact of COVID-19 on development prospects, and more.
